  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary objective of this treatment review and feedback program is to quantify the risk
      status for medication adherence in a cohort of Australian patients diagnosed with
      schizophrenia.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The primary objective of this treatment review and feedback program is to quantify the risk
      status for medication adherence in a cohort of Australian patients diagnosed with
      schizophrenia. Observational study - no study drug administered
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
