    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Clinical diagnosis of schizophrenia or schizoaffective disorder according to DSM-IV

          -  Currently treated in an outpatient clinic

          -  Able to provide informed consent

          -  Concurrent enrolment in clinical trials is acceptable

          -  Have completed all questions on the Drug Attitude Inventory (DAI-10) and Medication
             Adherence Rating Scale (MARS) survey

        Exclusion Criteria:
      </textblock>
